<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Youth Mental Health Forum</title>
 
  <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
 <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="styles.css">
 <body>
    <%- include('header.ejs'); %>
<section class="container mt-5">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <h2 class="text-center">Youth Mental Health Forum Board</h2>
      <hr>
      <ul class="forum-board">
        <li>
          <h4>General Discussion</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Welcome and Introductions: New to the forum? Introduce yourself here and get to know other members.</li>
            <li>General Mental Health Chat: Discuss any topics related to mental health and well-being that don't fit into specific categories.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>Anxiety and Stress</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Coping Strategies: Share and discover various techniques for managing anxiety and stress.</li>
            <li>Anxiety Stories: Share your personal experiences with anxiety and how you've managed it.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
             <li>
          <h4>Depression Support</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Seeking Help and Support: Connect with others to find mutual support for dealing with depression.</li>
            <li>Recovery and Treatment: Discuss different treatments, therapies, and recovery stories.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>School and Academic Pressure</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Study Tips and Techniques: Exchange effective study methods, time management skills, and tips for academic success.</li>
            <li>Balancing School and Life: Share advice on managing academic pressures alongside personal life.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>Relationships</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Family Dynamics: Discuss how family relationships affect your mental health and seek advice on dealing with family issues.</li>
            <li>Friendships and Social Life: Talk about the impact of friendships on your mental health and share tips on maintaining healthy social connections.</li>
            <li>Romantic Relationships: Share experiences, seek advice, and discuss how romantic relationships influence your mental well-being.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>Self-Care and Wellness</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Daily Self-Care Practices: Share routines and tips for maintaining mental and physical health.</li>
            <li>Mindfulness and Meditation: Discuss mindfulness practices, meditation techniques, and their benefits.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>Creative Corner</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Art and Expression: Share your artwork, writing, music, or other creative projects.</li>
            <li>Inspirations and Ideas: Discuss what inspires you and exchange creative ideas with others.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>Resource Sharing</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Books and Articles: Recommend books, articles, and other reading materials that have helped you.</li>
            <li>Videos and Podcasts: Share videos, podcasts, and other media related to mental health.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

